          What does the Q in Lgbtq stand for?
          Queer and/or Questioning
          The acronym stands for lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender. At times, a Q will be added for Queer and/or Questioning, an A for Ally, an I for Intersex and/or a TS for Two- Spirit. Lesbian a woman whose primary romantic, emotional and physical attractions are to other women.

          What does it mean to queer a text?
          Queering is the verb form of the word queer and comes from the shortened version of the phrase "queer reading." It is a technique that came out of queer theory in the late 1980s through the 1990s and is used as a way to challenge heteronormativity by analyzing places in a text that use heterosexuality or identity ...
